==English==

===Noun===
'''lock'''

# something used for [[fasten]]ing, which can only be opened with a [[key]] or [[combination]]
# a segment of a [[canal]] enclosed by gates, used for raising and lowering boats between levels
# a tuft of [[hair]]
# the firing mechanism of a [[gun]]
# A means of traversing from a higher water level to a lower one, or vice versa, by controlling the flow of water into and out of an enclosed area.

